# ez_MATH

下载文件后打开：

```cpp
#include<stdio.h>
#include<string.h>
int main()
{
	//welcome to XUPT_CTF!
	//在CTF逆向中，首先需要建立起逆向思维，希望本次CTF校赛能够给你带来一些收获！
	char flag[] = 'xxx';
	for (int i = 0; i < strlen(flag); i++)
	{
		//printf('%c', flag[i]);
		flag[i] -= 5;
		flag[i] += 2;
		flag[i] -= 1;
		flag[i] ^= 5;
		flag[i] += 2;
		flag[i] = (flag[i] + 1);
		printf('%d,', flag[i]);
	}
}
//encodeflag = {106, 112, 91, 105, 117, 79, 91, 120, 100, 97, 67, 109, 97, 71, 71, 71, 91, 109, 115, 127}
```

提示加密后的flag为：

```cpp
encodeflag = {106, 112, 91, 105, 117, 79, 91, 120, 100, 97, 67, 109, 97, 71, 71, 71, 91, 109, 115, 127}
```

经过逆推后的代码是：

```cpp
int s[] = {106, 112, 91, 105, 117, 79, 91, 120, 100, 97, 67, 109, 97, 71, 71, 71, 91, 109, 115, 127};
int main(void){
	for (int i = 0; i < 20; i++)
	{
		s[i]--;
		s[i]-=2;
		s[i]^=5;
		s[i]+=1;
		s[i]-=2;
		s[i]+=5;
		printf('%c',s[i]);
	}
} 
```

